      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition. The exterior has significant damage including deep scratches, multiple dents, and paint deterioration across several panels. The interior shows heavy wear with damaged upholstery, scuffed surfaces, and some components that are not fully functional. Mechanical issues may be present and should be inspected prior to purchase.",
